<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Notebook Entry</div>
<dl id="n40080c"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n40" href="#n40080c">N40 (VI.B.28B)</a>:  <a href="../../FF/fnbs/n40all.htm#n40080c"> 80(c)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> Sodom / Gomorrhah / Adama / Zeboim / Zohar</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources">We find the earliest written notices of the Vice <font color="green">[sodomy]</font> in the mythical destruction of the Pentapolis (Gen. xix.), Sodom, Gomorrah (= &lsquo;&Aacute;mirah,&rsquo; the cultivated country), Adama, Zebo&iuml;m, and Zoar or Bela. <small> Richard F. Burton, &ldquo;Terminal Essay&rdquo;, <a name="RBTE2" href="../../FF/fdra/fdex.htm#RBTE2"><cite title="source">The Book of the Thousand Nights and a Night</cite></a> (n.d.) X, 227</small></blockquote> </dd></dl>
